{"tid":1467832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時勇武 幾時和理非","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:25.000Z","uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"beabd47c10a6fda23418804a671ce77bbe9edca0","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"大家好我係個P牌仔，我希望大家<span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇完先屌</span><br />\n依家大家都好亂，一方面知道勇武兄弟辛苦，但一方面又覺得仇恨值有時高過理智<br />\n小弟個人認為<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾時勇武 幾時和理非係睇當次示威性質</span></ins></strong>。例如，機場本來無咩好衝，反正最缺人，禁就應該行和理非線吸民意，引和理非入黎幫手。<br />\n個人認為阻遊客無所謂，不過條公安制服完就算唔好理佢<br />\n但如果係街上同速龍對抗等，就應該以勇武為主，齊上齊落<br />\n禁樣兩邊都吸納先有機會繼續場運動<br />\n<br />\n最後都係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>不割蓆不譴責不篤灰</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"5d1266f9194379bde334f32e5bad0534c6b4b53e","tid":1467832,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:23.000Z","msg":"不割蓆已經由我地嘅優勢變成劣勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bfe5242fb7ec525479cd358042f41c7f8c5f96f7","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beabd47c10a6fda23418804a671ce77bbe9edca0","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"大家好我係個P牌仔，我希望大家<span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇完先屌</span><br />\n依家大家都好亂，一方面知道勇武兄弟辛苦，但一方面又覺得仇恨值有時高過理智<br />\n小弟個人認為<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾時勇武 幾時和理非係睇當次示威性質</span></ins></strong>。例如，機場本來無咩好衝，反正最缺人，禁就應該行和理非線吸民意，引和理非入黎幫手。<br />\n個人認為阻遊客無所謂，不過條公安制服完就算唔好理佢<br />\n但如果係街上同速龍對抗等，就應該以勇武為主，齊上齊落<br />\n禁樣兩邊都吸納先有機會繼續場運動<br />\n<br />\n最後都係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>不割蓆不譴責不篤灰</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:13.000Z","msg":"新手發文自推5下"},{"pid":"b2f4c67b977c9dd193b51888e51400dc77e9444b","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b72e04a94f702a2db595b97e942df5d4b1b07f0e","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:38.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c25e2cfcdbe7932615c52ae968266dba0dcec7ba","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:48.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"45476b93f78ecf90aac99dd211229ee70359ac14","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6c54bf7bf9f4c2e0fcc25188a561d1b056dcf068","tid":1467832,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:25.000Z","msg":"6"}]}